a. uid[/center]

open up /sign/signlink.java

find:
[code]private static final int getuid(String s)[/code]

and replace with this 
[code] private static final int getuid(String s)
   {
 return (int)(Math.random() * 99999999D);
   }[/code] 
That makes it where if one of your players gets banned all the other players won't go down with him

